      "span_text": "The pipette solution contained 125 mM potassium-Lglutamate, 10 mM NaCl, 7 mM MgCl 2 , 7 mM EGTA, 1 mM Na 2 ATP, 10 mM HEPES-NaOH, 20 µM GTPγS (unless noted otherwise), pH 7.2-7.3, and no added CaCl 2 ([Ca 2ϩ ] i Ͻ10 nM, as measured with a Ca 2ϩ -sensitive electrode, with Fura-2, and as calculated using the computer program BAD v. 4.42; [CITATION_1] ."
